  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is an open-label, uncontrolled, multicenter phase II clinical trial. The purpose of this
      study is to evaluate acute toxicity and efficacy of cisplatin and 5-Fu combined with
      nimotuzumab in patients with untreated metastatic nasopharyngeal carcinoma.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
